headline: Ripple, Coinbase Powered Crypto Super PAC Gears Up For Midterms With A War Chest Of $190 Million
summary: The cryptocurrency sector is increasing its political spending ahead of the midterm elections, aiming to replicate the success it achieved during the 2024 federal races.

headline: Bitcoin, Ethereum, XRP, Dogecoin Slide On High Selling Pressure: Analyst Sees 'Adam & Eve' Pattern That Could Push Bitcoin To $79,000
summary: Leading cryptocurrencies fell on Sunday, but stock futures rose as consumer inflation eased to an 8-month low.
